'''Batabanó Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in the 64th street in [[Batabanó, Cuba|Batabanó]], [[Cuba]]. It was established as a museum on 2 February 1982.<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/403 Museo Municipal de Batabanó]</ref>

The museum holds collections on archeology, history and weaponry.

